title: Matt Birk & Vikings OL Coach Barone at Training Camp w/ PA
description: Two-time All-Pro, six-time Pro Bowl selection, Super Bowl champion and former Minnesota Viking, Matt Birk as well as current Vikings' Offensive Line Coach Clancy Barone, join PA and friends at the final week of training camp.
